<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; color: #374151; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f9fafb; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1); overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #6366f1; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
    .body { padding: 32px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #6366f1; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 16px 32px; background: #f3f4f6; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header"><h1>NiceTasker</h1></div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p><strong><%= @inviter.display_name %></strong> has invited you to collaborate on the board <strong>"<%= @board.name %>"</strong>.</p>
      <p>Click the button below to accept the invitation and join the board:</p>
      <div style="text-align:center">
        <a class="btn" href="<%= @accept_url %>">Accept Invitation</a>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">This invitation expires in 7 days. If you weren't expecting it, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">NiceTasker — Your team's task board</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
